Summary

This Streamlit page (1_NPS_Log_Upload.py) is a full-width NPS Log Upload dashboard with login protection.

Features:

Login/Authentication

Uses check_auth() from auth.py to protect the page.

Sidebar File Uploads

Upload .log files â†’ automatically converts to CSV and saves in ~/nps_app/csv/nps.

Upload .csv files â†’ simply saves for historical view.

Historical Data View

Reads all CSVs in the CSV directory.

Concatenates them into a single DataFrame.

Sorts by timestamp and displays in a maximized table.

Existing CSV Files List

Displays all CSV files with filename, last modified, and size.

Searchable and sortable table.

Download button for each CSV file.

Layout

Maximized width using st.set_page_config(layout="wide").

Sidebar remains for uploads; main page displays historical data and CSV info.

